{"tid":2101982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【天譴】大批蝗蟲入侵中国西南；湖北江西多處河川潰堤！","createTime":"2020-07-10T07:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T13:31:50.000Z","uid":293677,"like":179,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"dbcf4ca7efc030f54ef5b37ebd697229e4832205","tid":2101982,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:06:12.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8Dnjhh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8Dnjhh.png&h=5849fbb8&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgTq1v7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgTq1v7.png&h=437ca8d7&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3223959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3223959&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=6850d532\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3223959&h=2683fae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3223959</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-07-10 13:01:20<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">大批蝗蟲由寮國入侵中國西南一帶，雲南普洱市林業和草原局證實，黃脊竹蝗持續入侵態勢嚴重，目前已近10萬畝面積的林、農地受害</span></span>，當局坦承7至9月份黃脊竹蝗暴發成災的可能性大。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，雲南普洱市遭遇蝗災，上月28日首度發現黃脊竹蝗由寮國邊境入侵，現在災情逐漸擴大，當局表示現在蝗災發展趨勢蔓延，不但境外蝗蟲持續入侵態勢嚴重，每天都能監測到新入侵蟲群，同時在進入中國後擴散速度加快，有向周邊縣區蔓延趨勢，同時蝗蟲目標有蔓延至農田趨勢，對農作物存在潛在災害風險。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3223887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3223887&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=95730baf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3223887&h=f5909ac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3223887</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/07/10/phpFtMOUH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F07%2F10%2FphpFtMOUH.jpg&h=b7854b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/07/10/phpKHh0xB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F07%2F10%2FphpKHh0xB.jpg&h=f37dd412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020-07-10 12:30:28<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國長江流域近日暴雨不斷，造成嚴重洪災。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">中國湖北省、江西省8日至9日期間接連發生多起河川潰堤災情，合計逾2萬名村民受到威脅，洪水淹沒超過3萬畝農田。截至9日晚間，部分堤防破口仍持續擴大，就連中國官媒央視也坦承「形勢嚴峻」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，湖北省武穴市花橋鎮荊竹河8日上午發生潰堤，堤防破口長約40公尺，造成下游4個村莊共6000名村民受到威脅，洪水淹沒當地逾1萬畝農田，積水深度約1公尺。中國《央視》9日報導指出，經連夜搶修，堤防破口僅封堵約一半，「從現場水流情況看，目前形勢依然較嚴峻」。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RRhCSCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRRhCSCH.jpg&h=d4bd871b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"orange\">唔好俾佢停</span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">天譴係會繼續黎</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"xx-large\">天譴係會繼續黎</span></span>"},{"pid":"6536d1d29573220dfbb612d1c404a95e8d2c9e3f","tid":2101982,"uid":12628,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"儲齊十災未"},{"pid":"6ee37fa58687693c465f1c26960500030dc37260","tid":2101982,"uid":231480,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0