/>\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RRhCSCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRRhCSCH.jpg&h=d4bd871b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"orange\">唔好俾佢停</span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">天譴係會繼續黎</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"xx-large\">天譴係會繼續黎</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"我見過啲蝗蟲手臂咁大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea282c5c8c934484fff1e5846a1de16fe9081cf","tid":2101982,"uid":21141,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2eSLg9W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2eSLg9W.png&h=08bac519&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f05a8addb192c0f5cd3d49cfb7a520789c15d8d7","tid":2101982,"uid":191661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"聽講蝗蟲有山埃，食左會中毒<br />\n無得補充蛋白質了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caf6dcaf82a126c7966f4351ffd09dbf4320c8d","tid":2101982,"uid":28759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:26:02.000Z","msg":"蝗災同水災係相輔相乘<br />\n<br />\n濕土有利蝗蟲繁殖<br />\n植物枯竭造就水土流失 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f3fd766840728d34d95350062ef59ed0c7441e","tid":2101982,"uid":39200,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"無事啦<br />\n原來以為洪水攪到無哂農作物會唔夠野食<br />\n依家無啦啦有野食自己飛入國補給呀, 虫食蟲, 仲有營養"},{"pid":"0122eb2f09786af60f29fb3270b1dae29ce2b836","tid":2101982,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>多</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"62938ba3